data.description: Beautifully Maintained Townhome Located Within A Few Miles of Two State Parks! Featuring a Private & Attached 1 Car Garage. As You Enter You Are Welcomed Into the Spacious & Open Living Area. Dining Room Has Small Balcony To Let In That Fresh Air & Natural Lighting That Will Lift Any Mood. Kitchen Features Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Built In Microwave & Pantry For Additional Storage. Bedrooms On Opposite Ends Provide The Perfect Layout For A Sense of Privacy. Primary Bedroom W/ Walk-In Closet & Private En-Suite w/ Double Sinks & Subway Tiled Shower. Located Within Walking Distance to Galaxy Park For A Brisk Walk, OR Drive 15 Mins to The Local's Favorite Floyd Lamb State Park. Located Within Minutes of Aliante Golf Club, Gilcrease Orchard, Ice Age Fossils State Park, Aliante Casino, Tons of Shopping Centers and the 215. There Is NO Shortage Of Things To Do - Whether You're An Outdoors Person or Entertainment Person, 4655 Flower Moon #101 Is Your Key To It All!
